Scope: this adapter targets only the MIT-licensed pieces under the
activepieces monorepo paths `packages/pieces/{framework,common,core,community}/**`.
It does NOT bundle, redistribute, or execute code from the proprietary
Enterprise Edition paths (`packages/ee/**` and
`packages/server/api/src/app/ee/**`). Operators are responsible for installing
only MIT-licensed piece packages into this worker.

Each piece may bring its own third-party dependencies (e.g. official SDKs for
Slack, Gmail, Stripe). Those dependencies carry their own licenses, which are
preserved in the installed node_modules tree.
